{"tid":1919212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［口罩真假］最近係不同藥房都見到依隻口罩","createTime":"2020-03-10T15:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T17:46:06.000Z","uid":118056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"508bdc34206ae3c47a539325ae61b801f8004711","tid":1919212,"uid":118056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"有無人知依隻口罩係真定假？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近係唔同藥房都見到依隻聲稱日本牌子既口罩<br />\n點知買左先發現佢入面連膠袋都無個 而且口罩好薄身<br />\n有試過剪開係有3層 搵水撒係上面都無過底<br />\n但中間個層一搵火燒就著而唔係熔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燒完仲好臭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdmq56C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhdmq56C.png&h=a45f48ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最吊鬼係我同屋企人係唔同藥房都買到依款口罩 但各自既包裝都唔同<br />\n我係銅鑼灣買到既盒內無膠袋裝住口罩<br />\n屋企人買既就有膠袋裝住<br />\n<br />\n純粹個人猜測：會唔會有黑商9印堆盒用黎放來源不清楚既口罩去賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48c2cea7a1118132c64d73dd506096d9a661d1b","tid":1919212,"uid":118056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:37:21.000Z","msg":"補充：屋企人係青衣買到"},{"pid":"e1c050644796a3ce03cba729227ea7acb14e602b","tid":1919212,"uid":118056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7ff6ab76ee18355f8ff0bf7f9f816743963469","tid":1919212,"uid":615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"fake啦<br />\n日本仲有得出口咩"},{"pid":"2a3405b3cbcf7ba3d13c715f38da22b93ec78510","tid":1919212,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"唔好諗啦<br />\n唔係出入醫院都夠用"},{"pid":"1d3aeee929a37bf9fe330c8deb6ee16f8672298c","tid":1919212,"uid":335063,"like":0,